Natalya Petrova (née Kokulenko; amụrụ ya na ọwa 16 Nọvemba 1957) Ọ bụ nwanyị emba Russia ọ bu onye na-agba ọsọ track and field hurdler onye na-asọ mpi maka Soviet Union na 100 mita hurdles

Ọ nọchitere anya mba ya na 1983 World Championships in Athletics na ahu 1982 European Athletics Indoor Championships, na-emecha nke anọ n'oge abụọ ahụ. Ọ bụ onye nwetara ọtụtụ ihe nrite ọla edo na sprint hurdles na ahụ 1983 Universiade.

Ọ bụ onye mmeri mba otu oge, ebe ọ meriri ihe mgbochi mita 60 na 1982 Soviet Indoor Championships. O nwetara ihe kachasị mma ya na World Championships na 1983, na-agba ọsọ nke 12.83 sekọnd na iru eru.
